2025-06-16T19:59:49.963770+00:00 app[web.1]: P1, P2, P3, or NO_RESPONSE_REQUIRED
2025-06-16T19:59:49.963771+00:00 app[web.1]:

2025-06-16T19:59:49.963772+00:00 app[web.1]: So for example if it's something that you think is between a P3 and P2, then better to go with
2025-06-16T19:59:49.963772+00:00 app[web.1]: a P2.
2025-06-16T19:59:49.963772+00:00 app[web.1]: 
2025-06-16T19:59:49.963773+00:00 app[web.1]: P1:
2025-06-16T19:59:49.963773+00:00 app[web.1]: - Something urgent that requires an immediate response.

2025-06-16T19:59:49.963775+00:00 app[web.1]: P2:
2025-06-16T19:59:49.963776+00:00 app[web.1]: - Power outage.
2025-06-16T19:59:49.963776+00:00 app[web.1]: - Water heater is not working.
2025-06-16T19:59:49.963776+00:00 app[web.1]: 
2025-06-16T19:59:49.963776+00:00 app[web.1]: P3:
2025-06-16T19:59:49.963776+00:00 app[web.1]: - Not an urgent problem, more of a question or a thankyou that should require a "you're welcome"
2025-06-16T19:59:49.963777+00:00 app[web.1]: - A request for a late checkout or early checkin
2025-06-16T19:59:49.963777+00:00 app[web.1]: - A request for a refund or a discount
2025-06-16T19:59:49.963777+00:00 app[web.1]: - A request to schedule a complimentary cleaning
2025-06-16T19:59:49.963778+00:00 app[web.1]: - Recommendations for food or places to visit.
2025-06-16T19:59:49.963778+00:00 app[web.1]: - When they send passports or identification documents.
2025-06-16T19:59:49.963778+00:00 app[web.1]: 
2025-06-16T19:59:49.963778+00:00 app[web.1]: NO_RESPONSE_REQUIRED:
2025-06-16T19:59:49.963778+00:00 app[web.1]: - When conversation has come to a natural conclusion.
2025-06-16T19:59:49.963779+00:00 app[web.1]: - When the guest is just saying thank you or goodbye and a "you're welcome" is not appropriate
